WEBVTT

00:01.532 --> 00:03.474
BENNY, YOU OKAY?

00:03.474 --> 00:06.277
I´VE BEEN BURNING UP
ALL DAY.

00:06.277 --> 00:08.679
WELL, YOU DO FEEL
HOT AND CLAMMY.

00:08.679 --> 00:09.740
OH.

00:09.740 --> 00:12.113
THAT´S JUST THE TOP HALF.

00:16.487 --> 00:19.019
DO YOU HAVE
ANY OTHER SYMPTOMS?

00:19.019 --> 00:20.651
IRRITABILITY.

00:20.651 --> 00:23.023
ANY NEW SYMPTOMS?

00:24.655 --> 00:27.498
YOU KNOW, FEMALE STUFF.

00:27.498 --> 00:32.333
WELL, BENNY,
YOU MIGHT BE AT THAT AGE.

00:32.333 --> 00:34.105
THIS COULD BE
THE BEGINNING OF MENOPAUSE.

00:34.105 --> 00:35.436
NO, NO, NO.

00:35.436 --> 00:37.608
I JUST STARTED DATING
A 42-YEAR-OLD GUY.

00:37.608 --> 00:39.770
I CAN´T BE GOING
THROUGH THE CHANGE.

00:39.770 --> 00:41.812
BENNY, IT´S NOT THE END
OF THE WORLD.

00:41.812 --> 00:43.574
THE GYNECOLOGIST
CAN HELP YOU.

00:43.574 --> 00:45.616
THERE´S PILLS
FOR THE INCONTINENCE,

00:45.616 --> 00:47.748
HORMONE CREAMS
TO RESTORE LUBRICATION.

00:47.748 --> 00:49.380
[ RETCHES ]

00:58.729 --> 01:00.731
HEY, NO VOMIT.

01:00.731 --> 01:04.135
HONEY, I´M TRYING TO TALK YOUR
MOM INTO SEEING THE DOCTOR.

01:04.135 --> 01:06.267
SHE MIGHT BE GOING
THROUGH THE CHANGE.

01:06.267 --> 01:08.799
HEY, YOU DON´T HAVE TO TELL
EVERYBODY ABOUT THIS.

01:08.799 --> 01:12.143
I DON´T WANT PEOPLE TO THINK
I AM LESS THAN A WOMAN.

01:12.143 --> 01:14.405
YEAH, GOD FORBID
THAT SECRET GETS OUT.

01:15.606 --> 01:19.280
WHEN WAS THE LAST TIME
YOU SAW YOUR GYNECOLOGIST?

01:19.280 --> 01:21.112
OH, IT´S BEEN
A FEW YEARS.

01:21.112 --> 01:22.713
HOW MANY YEARS?

01:22.713 --> 01:24.515
WELL, LET´S SEE.

01:24.515 --> 01:28.259
I WAS LYING ON MY BACK, FULL
OF DRUGS, GEORGE WAS CRYING,

01:28.259 --> 01:31.722
SO IT WAS EITHER
THE DAY HE WAS BORN

01:31.722 --> 01:34.595
OR CHRISTMAS 1973.

01:37.298 --> 01:40.201
YOU HAVEN´T BEEN
TO THE DOCTOR IN 37 YEARS?

01:40.201 --> 01:42.133
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

01:44.435 --> 01:46.577
COME ON. THEY ALWAYS FIND
SOMETHING WRONG WITH YOU.

01:46.577 --> 01:48.809
THAT´S HOW
THEY MAKE THEIR MONEY.

01:48.809 --> 01:50.841
LOOK, MOM,
IF THERE´S A PROBLEM,

01:50.841 --> 01:52.643
YOU GOT TO DEAL
WITH THIS, OKAY?

01:52.643 --> 01:54.715
YOU GOTTA GO
TO THE DOCTOR TOMORROW,

01:54.715 --> 01:56.317
EVEN IF I GOTTA TAKE YOU.

01:56.317 --> 02:00.321
YOU ARE GONNA TAKE ME
TO THE GYNECOLOGIST?

02:00.321 --> 02:03.123
YEAH, BUT I´M GONNA WEAR
MY HEADPHONES,

02:03.123 --> 02:05.756
SO I DON´T HEAR
THE GYNECOLOGIST SAY,

02:05.756 --> 02:08.599
"OH, MY GOD!
I QUIT!"

02:08.599 --> 02:12.403
[ INTRO TO WAR´S
"LOW RIDER" PLAYS ]

02:22.243 --> 02:29.320
♫ ALL MY FRIENDS
KNOW THE LOW RIDER ♫

02:56.407 --> 02:58.178
[ RHYTHMIC DRUMMING ]

02:58.178 --> 03:01.652
WELL, MOM AND I ARE OFF
TO THE GYNO.

03:03.214 --> 03:04.585
LOOK AT YOU.

03:04.585 --> 03:06.287
YOU´RE ALL DRESSED UP.

03:06.287 --> 03:08.719
WELL, I FIGURED
I´D FEEL LESS CHEAP

03:08.719 --> 03:12.863
IF I HAD SOME NICE HEELS
IN THE STIRRUPS.

03:12.863 --> 03:15.796
WELL, MOM AND I ARE OFF
TO THE GYNO.

03:15.796 --> 03:17.498
[ DRUMMING CONTINUES ]

03:19.530 --> 03:22.202
HEY, MAMBO KINGS,
OYE, CóMO VA?

03:22.202 --> 03:25.476
GRANDPA´S TEACHING ME
THE SECRETS OF THE CONGA.

03:25.476 --> 03:28.979
AH, LISTEN TO
THE HEARTBEAT OF CUBA, EH?

03:28.979 --> 03:31.442
KA-KU KA-KU
KA-KU KU-YE

03:31.442 --> 03:33.444
Both:
KA-KU KA-KU KA-KU KU-YE

03:33.444 --> 03:35.746
[ LAUGHS ]

03:35.746 --> 03:39.650
CAN´T ONE RAFT OF HORN PLAYERS
MAKE IT TO MIAMI?

03:39.650 --> 03:42.923
THANK YOU, MOMMY.
YOU WON´T REGRET THIS.

03:42.923 --> 03:45.496
WHAT WON´T
YOUR MOTHER REGRET?

03:45.496 --> 03:47.458
LISTEN, DADDY...

03:47.458 --> 03:49.760
I KNOW MOM WAS UNFAITHFUL,

03:49.760 --> 03:51.862
BUT I THINK THE TWO OF YOU
CAN WORK THIS OUT

03:51.862 --> 03:54.265
IF YOU CAN JUST SIT DOWN
IN THE SAME ROOM TOGETHER.

03:54.265 --> 03:55.466
NO, MI´JITA.

03:55.466 --> 03:57.538
THERE´S NOTHING
TO WORK OUT, EH?

03:57.538 --> 03:59.610
IT´S OVER.
IT´S DONE.

03:59.610 --> 04:02.673
IT´S DEADER
THAN CASTRO´S EYES.

04:02.673 --> 04:05.916
DADDY, IF IT WERE
REALLY OVER,

04:05.916 --> 04:09.350
WOULD SHE BE FLYING HERE
TOMORROW NIGHT TO SEE YOU?

04:09.350 --> 04:11.452
SHE´S FLYING HERE?

04:11.452 --> 04:12.723
YES.

04:12.723 --> 04:14.725
SO, YOU´LL TALK TO HER?

04:14.725 --> 04:16.927
ABSOLUTELY.

04:16.927 --> 04:18.459
THANK YOU, DADDY.

04:18.459 --> 04:21.432
IT´LL BE A PLEASURE
TO TELL HER TO HER FACE

04:21.432 --> 04:26.697
THAT SHE´S A LYING,
CHEATING...JEZEBEL

04:26.697 --> 04:29.400
WHO WILL BURN IN HELL
WITH HER LOVER,

04:29.400 --> 04:32.403
BOILING IN A SOUP
OF THEIR OWN TREACHERY.

04:34.775 --> 04:37.778
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

04:48.419 --> 04:49.960
THIS IS AWKWARD, HUH?

04:49.960 --> 04:52.693
I´M HERE
WITH MY MOM, TOO.

04:54.525 --> 04:55.966
I´M HIS WIFE.

04:57.528 --> 04:58.929
STILL AWKWARD.

05:07.538 --> 05:09.710
MOM, YOU ALL RIGHT?

05:09.710 --> 05:11.512
NO, NO, NOT REALLY.

05:11.512 --> 05:13.444
COME ON, YOU´RE TAKING THIS
TOO HARD.

05:13.444 --> 05:15.646
EVERY WOMAN GOES
THROUGH THE CHANGE.

05:15.646 --> 05:17.017
IT´S NOTHING
TO BE ASHAMED OF.

05:17.017 --> 05:19.820
GEORGE, I GOT THE CLAP!

05:28.459 --> 05:29.830
WHAT?

05:29.830 --> 05:33.063
MOM, YOU´RE OLD ENOUGH
TO BE RESPONSIBLE.

05:33.063 --> 05:36.066
HOW COULD YOU LET
THIS HAPPEN?

05:36.066 --> 05:38.038
DID RANDY PRESSURE YOU
INTO DOING SOMETHING

05:38.038 --> 05:40.571
YOU WERE
UNCOMFORTABLE WITH?

05:40.571 --> 05:42.873
HE DID.

05:42.873 --> 05:45.345
HE TOLD ME
THAT IT WOULD BE OKAY

05:45.345 --> 05:48.519
AND THAT ALL THE COOL GRANDMAS
ARE DOING IT.

05:48.519 --> 05:51.452
I´M GONNA KILL HIM
FOR GIVING ME THIS.

05:51.452 --> 05:54.084
THIS IS WHY I DIDN´T WANT YOU
TO DATE. MOM, YOU´RE TOO OLD.

05:54.084 --> 05:57.688
YOU SHOULD BE CLOSING UP
THE SHOP BY NOW.

05:57.688 --> 05:59.590
WELL, THE SHOP
IS STILL OPEN,

05:59.590 --> 06:02.533
AND NOW THERE´S A CLEANUP
IN AISLE TWO!

06:07.137 --> 06:09.540
MRS. LOPEZ.
WHAT?

06:09.540 --> 06:12.543
YOU DIDN´T COMPLETE SOME
QUESTIONS ON YOUR RECORD.

06:12.543 --> 06:14.074
WOULD YOU LIKE
TO COME BACK INSIDE?

06:14.074 --> 06:16.477
NO, LET´S DO IT OUT HERE.

06:16.477 --> 06:21.081
THE LAST TIME I WENT IN THERE,
YOU GUYS GAVE ME THE DRIPSIES.

06:21.081 --> 06:23.884
SEE, YOUR BIRTH DATE --
YOU ONLY WROTE A 4.

06:23.884 --> 06:25.456
GIMME.

06:27.858 --> 06:31.391
OKAY.
AND YOUR SECOND PREGNANCY --

06:31.391 --> 06:33.424
NOW, DID YOU CARRY THAT
TO FULL TERM?

06:37.498 --> 06:39.169
SECOND PREGNANCY?

06:39.169 --> 06:42.903
MOM, WHAT THE HELL
IS SHE TALKING ABOUT?

06:42.903 --> 06:44.435
YOU KNOW WHAT?

06:44.435 --> 06:46.036
I FORGOT TO TELL YOU
YOU HAVE A SISTER.

06:46.036 --> 06:49.039
LET´S FINISH
THIS INSIDE.

06:49.039 --> 06:50.841
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

06:54.014 --> 06:55.586
YOU´RE NOT GONNA
BELIEVE THIS, ANGIE.

06:55.586 --> 06:57.618
I JUST FOUND OUT
MY MOM GAVE AWAY A SISTER

06:57.618 --> 06:58.789
I NEVER KNEW THAT I HAD.

06:58.789 --> 07:00.020
GEORGE.
NO, WAIT.

07:00.020 --> 07:01.492
IT GETS BETTER.

07:01.492 --> 07:03.153
THE ONLY WAY
THAT I FOUND OUT

07:03.153 --> 07:06.527
IS BECAUSE
MY MOM HAS GONORRHEA.

07:06.527 --> 07:09.530
GEORGE, THIS IS JANET.

07:09.530 --> 07:11.662
SHE´S A CUSTOMER.

07:16.937 --> 07:18.539
I´M SHOWING HER SUNSCREENS

07:18.539 --> 07:20.541
BECAUSE SHE´S TAKING
A LOVELY TRIP TO MEXICO.

07:20.541 --> 07:24.144
HOW WOULD YOU FEEL ABOUT TAKING
AN ITCHY OLD LADY WITH YOU?

07:29.620 --> 07:32.523
JUST TAKE THE SUNSCREEN.
I´LL BILL YOU LATER.

07:34.825 --> 07:36.557
WHAT IS GOING ON?

07:36.557 --> 07:40.090
FIRST, YOU HAVE A FATHER,
AND NOW YOU HAVE A SISTER.

07:40.090 --> 07:43.834
HOW MANY FAMILY MEMBERS
ARE YOU HIDING FROM HIM?

07:43.834 --> 07:46.667
YOU KNOW WHAT?
DON´T JUDGE ME.

07:46.667 --> 07:49.640
AFTER MANNY WALKED OUT ON US,
THEN I FOUND OUT I WAS PREGNANT.

07:49.640 --> 07:51.842
I ALREADY HAD A 2-YEAR-OLD
AND NO MONEY.

07:51.842 --> 07:53.674
I DID WHAT I HAD TO DO.

07:53.674 --> 07:56.577
SO YOU GAVE UP MY SISTER,
JUST LIKE THAT?

07:56.577 --> 08:00.080
I MADE SURE
SHE WENT TO A GOOD FAMILY.

08:00.080 --> 08:03.483
WHY DIDN´T YOU
DO THAT FOR ME?

08:11.061 --> 08:12.993
HAVE YOU STAYED
IN TOUCH WITH HER?

08:12.993 --> 08:14.865
DOES SHE EVEN KNOW
ABOUT US?

08:14.865 --> 08:16.867
OH, CRAP.
HERE WE GO.

08:16.867 --> 08:19.199
MOM, THIS IS MY SISTER.
I WANT TO KNOW ABOUT HER.

08:19.199 --> 08:21.672
WHAT´S THE NAME OF THE FAMILY
THAT ADOPTED HER?

08:21.672 --> 08:23.604
LET´S SEE.

08:23.604 --> 08:25.075
WAIT, WAIT.

08:25.075 --> 08:26.937
IT WAS MR. AND MRS.

08:26.937 --> 08:31.882
MIND-YOUR-OWN-BUSINESS
YOU´RE-LUCKY-I-KEPT- YOU -BERG.

08:31.882 --> 08:33.614
NAMES, MOM.

08:33.614 --> 08:35.746
FOR GOD´S SAKE.

08:35.746 --> 08:37.748
IT WAS THE LORENZOS.

08:37.748 --> 08:39.620
YOU ´MEMBER.

08:39.620 --> 08:42.152
THEY USED TO LIVE
DOWN THE STREET.

08:42.152 --> 08:44.795
DOES SHE KNOW
THAT SHE´S ADOPTED?

08:44.795 --> 08:46.196
HOW THE HELL SHOULD I KNOW?

08:46.196 --> 08:48.028
THEY MOVED OUT OF THE
NEIGHBORHOOD.

08:48.028 --> 08:50.130
I BET I CAN FIND THEM.

08:50.130 --> 08:52.162
NO, HEY, YOU KNOW WHAT?
YOU STAY OUT OF THIS.

08:52.162 --> 08:54.064
IT´S BETWEEN ME
AND YOUR FATHER.

08:54.064 --> 08:56.567
SO, MANNY KNOWS
ABOUT THIS?

08:56.567 --> 08:58.639
NO, IT´S BETWEEN
ME AND ME.

08:58.639 --> 08:59.910
LEAVE IT ALONE.

08:59.910 --> 09:01.171
LEAVE IT ALONE.

09:01.171 --> 09:04.114
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]
LEAVE IT ALONE.

09:07.648 --> 09:10.651
ALL RIGHT, WELL, THANKS A LOT.
I APPRECIATE IT.

09:10.651 --> 09:12.653
UH-HUH. BYE.

09:12.653 --> 09:14.785
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
I GOT UP EARLY.

09:14.785 --> 09:16.857
I´VE BEEN ON THE COMPUTER
FOR HOURS,

09:16.857 --> 09:18.328
SEARCHING
FOR YOUR SISTER.

09:18.328 --> 09:20.290
I CROSS-CHECKED EVERY LORENZO
IN CALIFORNIA

09:20.290 --> 09:22.332
WITH THE YEAR YOUR SISTER
WOULD HAVE BEEN BORN,

09:22.332 --> 09:24.234
AND I´VE NARROWED IT
DOWN TO 20.

09:24.234 --> 09:26.597
WELL, I SLEPT IN,

09:26.597 --> 09:29.069
TOOK A LONG SHOWER,
READ THE SPORTS PAGE,

09:29.069 --> 09:32.202
THEN I CALLED MY MOM´S
NEIGHBOR AND FOUND OUT
WHERE THE LORENZOS MOVED.

09:32.202 --> 09:34.805
IT´S THAT ONE RIGHT THERE.

09:36.707 --> 09:38.909
BUT LOOK AT YOU,
SURFING THE WEB.

09:38.909 --> 09:40.310
YOU ROCK!

09:42.212 --> 09:44.054
DID YOU CALL HER?

09:44.054 --> 09:45.686
NOT YET.

09:45.686 --> 09:47.618
I FOUND OUT SHE WORKS FOR
THE VALLEY SCHOOL DISTRICT.

09:47.618 --> 09:49.690
WHEN HER OFFICE OPENS,
I´M GONNA GO DOWN AND MEET HER.

09:49.690 --> 09:51.061
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA
SAY TO HER?

09:51.061 --> 09:52.793
I´M GONNA PLAY IT BY EAR.

09:52.793 --> 09:55.766
I MEAN, I GOT TO FIGURE OUT
WHETHER SHE KNOWS SHE´S ADOPTED.

09:55.766 --> 09:58.098
I´LL TAKE IT FROM THERE.

09:58.098 --> 10:00.771
BUT HER NAME´S LINDA.

10:00.771 --> 10:02.372
"HEY, GIVE ME 5 BUCKS,

10:02.372 --> 10:05.035
I´LL LET YOU WATCH
MY SISTER, LINDA, CHANGE."

10:09.910 --> 10:12.783
THAT SOUNDS NICE, HUH?

10:12.783 --> 10:16.216
OYE, MI´JITA,
CAN YOU IRON THIS SHIRT?

10:16.216 --> 10:17.718
SURE, DADDY.

10:17.718 --> 10:19.920
DID YOU TRIM
YOUR EYEBROWS?

10:19.920 --> 10:21.822
OH, JUST ONE...

10:23.854 --> 10:25.656
PUT AN ARCH IN IT...

10:25.656 --> 10:28.398
MAKES ME LOOK INTERESTED
WHEN PEOPLE ARE TALKING,

10:28.398 --> 10:31.401
AS IF I´M SAYING,
"IS THAT SO?"

10:35.335 --> 10:38.739
YOU´RE GONNA DRESS UP FOR MOM
TONIGHT, AREN´T YOU?

10:38.739 --> 10:42.142
THAT´S TONIGHT?
COMPLETELY FORGOT ABOUT IT.

10:42.142 --> 10:44.915
DADDY, I KNOW
WHEN YOU´RE LYING.

10:44.915 --> 10:47.778
IS THAT SO?

10:47.778 --> 10:49.419
ALL RIGHT, MI NIÑA.

10:49.419 --> 10:52.052
I WAS REHEARSING HOW I WAS GOING
TO TELL HER OFF,

10:52.052 --> 10:54.985
BUT THEN I GOT
TO THINKING.

10:54.985 --> 10:57.788
A MARRIAGE TAKES
TWO PEOPLE.

10:57.788 --> 10:58.929
MAYBE I WORKED TOO MUCH.

10:58.929 --> 11:00.831
MAYBE I NEGLECTED HER.

11:00.831 --> 11:03.193
MAYBE I DIDN´T TELL HER
ENOUGH HOW BEAUTIFUL SHE WAS,

11:03.193 --> 11:04.935
OR MAYBE I TOLD HER TOO MUCH.

11:04.935 --> 11:08.098
MAYBE YOU ANNOYED HER
INTO ANOTHER MAN´S ARMS.

11:10.240 --> 11:14.104
I HAVE A GOOD FEELING
ABOUT THIS, DADDY.

11:14.104 --> 11:17.177
WE ARE GONNA BE
A FAMILY AGAIN.

11:17.177 --> 11:20.050
AND, GEORGE,
HE´S GONNA MEET HIS SISTER

11:20.050 --> 11:23.784
FOR THE FIRST TIME
IN 35 YEARS.

11:23.784 --> 11:26.316
THIS IS SO BEAUTIFUL.

11:26.316 --> 11:28.789
MY MOM, MY DAD.

11:28.789 --> 11:30.861
YOU, YOUR SISTER.

11:30.861 --> 11:35.165
[ Voice breaking ] TWO FAMILIES
ARE COMING TOGETHER.

11:37.728 --> 11:39.369
ALL RIGHT,
I´LL CATCH YOU LATER.

11:44.805 --> 11:46.406
[ SNIFFLING ]

11:46.406 --> 11:49.810
OH, WHAT´S THE MATTER,
PRINCESS?

11:49.810 --> 11:52.142
YOU GAIN HALF A POUND?

11:55.085 --> 11:59.950
BENNY, THAT HURTS,
BUT IT DOESN´T BURN.

12:09.029 --> 12:10.831
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

12:10.831 --> 12:12.432
COME IN.

12:16.767 --> 12:17.808
LINDA LORENZO?

12:17.808 --> 12:19.810
YES. GEORGE LOPEZ?

12:19.810 --> 12:21.271
WE SPOKE ON THE PHONE.

12:21.271 --> 12:24.945
I´M WITH THE LATINO
ASSOCIATION OF DYSLEXICS.

12:28.879 --> 12:30.781
L.A.D.,
I THINK, RIGHT?

12:30.781 --> 12:32.082
HAVE A SEAT.

12:32.082 --> 12:33.924
LINDA LORENZO --

12:33.924 --> 12:37.187
I CAN´T BELIEVE I´M ACTUALLY
FACE-TO-FACE WITH MY OWN --

12:37.187 --> 12:41.391
SUPERINTENDENT
OF THE VALLEY SCHOOL DISTRICT.

12:41.391 --> 12:44.064
I NORMALLY DON´T TAKE
UNSCHEDULED MEETINGS,

12:44.064 --> 12:45.966
BUT YOUR CAUSE
HITS CLOSE TO HOME,

12:45.966 --> 12:47.998
BECAUSE I´M DYSLEXIC.

12:47.998 --> 12:50.200
YOU KNOW, ME TOO.

12:52.202 --> 12:54.074
IT MUST RUN IN YOUR FAMILY,
RIGHT?

12:54.074 --> 12:55.946
ACTUALLY, NOT.

12:55.946 --> 12:57.948
I KNOW
IT´S USUALLY GENETIC,

12:57.948 --> 13:00.550
BUT IT´S KIND OF A MYSTERY
WHERE MINE CAME FROM.

13:00.550 --> 13:02.282
AH.

13:04.214 --> 13:06.957
INTERESTING.

13:06.957 --> 13:10.220
YOU GOT A LOT OF PICTURES
OF YOUR FAMILY.

13:10.220 --> 13:13.163
YEAH, WE´RE VERY CLOSE.

13:13.163 --> 13:14.865
WOW,
THAT´S A NICE ONE.

13:14.865 --> 13:15.996
OH, YES.

13:15.996 --> 13:17.968
I MISS CUPCAKE SO MUCH.

13:17.968 --> 13:20.230
HE WAS MY CHILDHOOD PONY.

13:20.230 --> 13:22.973
YOU HAD A PONY?!

13:28.008 --> 13:31.041
I HAD TO SWIM
IN A TRASH CAN.

13:31.041 --> 13:33.043
WHAT?

13:33.043 --> 13:35.345
OH, I´M SORRY.
GULF WAR.

13:42.893 --> 13:45.125
MR. LOPEZ...

13:45.125 --> 13:47.527
WHAT CAN I DO
FOR YOUR ORGANIZATION?

13:47.527 --> 13:49.359
WELL, I THOUGHT THAT
SINCE WE´RE BOTH LATINOS

13:49.359 --> 13:50.861
AND THIS IS AN ISSUE --

13:50.861 --> 13:53.103
OH, ACTUALLY,
I´M NOT LATINA, I´M ITALIAN,

13:53.103 --> 13:55.305
BUT I GET THAT ALL THE TIME.

13:55.305 --> 13:56.967
[ CHUCKLES ]

13:56.967 --> 13:58.208
YOU THINK YOU´RE ITALIAN.

13:58.208 --> 14:00.941
I DON´T THINK I´M ITALIAN.

14:00.941 --> 14:02.142
I AM ITALIAN.

14:02.142 --> 14:04.014
SICILIANA.

14:04.014 --> 14:06.216
WE VISIT SICILY EVERY YEAR.

14:06.216 --> 14:07.948
WE GO TO THIS LITTLE CHURCH,

14:07.948 --> 14:10.350
WHERE MY MOTHER PRAYS
TO HER PATRON SAINT

14:10.350 --> 14:12.022
FOR HELPING TO CONCEIVE ME.

14:12.022 --> 14:14.885
SO, THIS ITALIAN WOMAN...

14:16.987 --> 14:18.858
SHE GAVE BIRTH TO YOU?

14:18.858 --> 14:20.460
YES.

14:20.460 --> 14:24.334
THAT´S WHY I CALL HER "MOM."

14:24.334 --> 14:27.037
YOU SEE,
THE REASON I ASK

14:27.037 --> 14:30.070
IS THAT A LOT OF DYSLEXIC KIDS
HAD UNHAPPY CHILDHOODS.

14:30.070 --> 14:33.473
DID YOU EVER WISH THAT
YOU HAD DIFFERENT PARENTS?

14:33.473 --> 14:35.105
NEVER.

14:35.105 --> 14:38.308
MY PARENTS GAVE ME SO MUCH LOVE
AND ENCOURAGEMENT.

14:38.308 --> 14:41.251
MY MOM EVEN QUIT WORK
TO TUTOR ME.

14:41.251 --> 14:44.214
I´M REALLY LUCKY.

14:51.021 --> 14:52.993
YEAH, YOU ARE.

14:52.993 --> 14:56.096
WELL, I THINK I´VE TAKEN
ENOUGH OF YOUR TIME.

14:56.096 --> 14:58.268
BUT WHAT ABOUT L.A.D.?

14:58.268 --> 15:01.901
FORGET ABOUT IT.
LET IT GO.

15:01.901 --> 15:03.373
WHAT´S THAT FOR?

15:03.373 --> 15:06.906
OH, IT´S FOR OUR
DYSLEXIA NEWSLETTER.

15:06.906 --> 15:08.478
IT´S ALL PICTURES.

15:15.345 --> 15:18.488
YOU TAKE CARE
OF YOURSELF...

15:23.593 --> 15:26.356
AND WATCH
YOUR BLOOD PRESSURE.

15:38.238 --> 15:39.569
I GOT YOUR MESSAGE.

15:39.569 --> 15:42.442
WHY AIN´T YOU AT WORK TODAY,
BABY DOLL?

15:42.442 --> 15:45.575
YOU DISGUSTING PIECE
OF CRAP!

15:45.575 --> 15:48.979
OH, WE´RE PLAYING
THAT GAME.

15:48.979 --> 15:52.682
ALL RIGHT, YOU DIRTY
LITTLE GARDEN GNOME!

15:52.682 --> 15:55.355
NO, YOU IDIOT!

15:55.355 --> 15:58.428
YOU GAVE ME AN STD.

15:58.428 --> 16:00.260
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

16:00.260 --> 16:01.992
YOU GAVE ME THE CLAP.

16:01.992 --> 16:04.194
NOW, WHO HAVE YOU BEEN
WHORING AROUND WITH, HUH?!

16:04.194 --> 16:07.437
JUST YOU, BENNY --
JUST YOU.

16:07.437 --> 16:10.700
YOU´RE THE BEST THING
THAT EVER HAPPENED TO ME.

16:10.700 --> 16:13.343
WHY WOULD I DO ANYTHING
TO MESS THAT UP?

16:13.343 --> 16:15.405
I SWEAR,
I DIDN´T KNOW I HAD IT.

16:15.405 --> 16:18.578
WELL, THE TRAMP
YOU WERE WITH BEFORE ME

16:18.578 --> 16:22.412
MUST HAVE GIVEN YOU
A LITTLE GOING-AWAY PRESENT.

16:22.412 --> 16:25.355
BENNY, I´M --
I´M SO SORRY.

16:25.355 --> 16:27.587
JUST TELL IT
TO THE CLINIC.

16:27.587 --> 16:31.291
YOU´RE GONNA BE TAKING
PENICILLIN FOR TWO WEEKS.

16:31.291 --> 16:33.663
MAYBE THIS IS A BLESSING.

16:33.663 --> 16:37.467
I MEAN, WE CAN JUST TALK
AND GET TO KNOW EACH OTHER

16:37.467 --> 16:39.099
AND REALLY OPEN UP.

16:41.201 --> 16:44.574
RIGHT, OR MAYBE YOU CAN CALL ME
WHEN YOU FINISHED YOUR MEDS

16:44.574 --> 16:47.637
AND BURNED THE BLANKET
IN THE BACK OF YOUR TRUCK!

16:47.637 --> 16:50.240
I´M GONNA MISS YOU, BABY.

16:50.240 --> 16:53.383
BACK OFF, OUTBREAK!
GET ON!

16:56.116 --> 16:57.687
DADDY, YOU LOOK GREAT.

16:57.687 --> 17:01.491
I DON´T THINK MOMMY´S GONNA
BE ABLE TO RESIST YOU.

17:01.491 --> 17:04.124
OOH, OH.

17:06.056 --> 17:08.758
I THINK YOU´RE TAKING THIS
A LITTLE TOO SERIOUSLY, VIC.

17:08.758 --> 17:11.801
WHY DON´T YOU TAKE SOME OF THAT
COLOGNE AND PUT IT ON A RAG,

17:11.801 --> 17:14.764
POP IT OVER HER MOUTH,
AND DRAG HER AWAY, HUH?

17:19.209 --> 17:22.472
PERHAPS I SHOULD AIR MYSELF OUT
IN THE BACKYARD.

17:24.444 --> 17:26.446
[ RETCHES ]

17:31.181 --> 17:33.123
HEY, NO VOMIT.

17:35.085 --> 17:37.827
HONEY, WHAT HAPPENED?
DID YOU MEET YOUR SISTER?

17:37.827 --> 17:39.159
WHAT?

17:39.159 --> 17:41.091
I TOLD YOU
TO LEAVE IT ALONE.

17:41.091 --> 17:42.392
WELL, I DIDN´T.

17:42.392 --> 17:44.094
AND I MET HER.

17:44.094 --> 17:46.696
AND SHE´S VERY HAPPY,
AND SHE´S VERY SUCCESSFUL.

17:46.696 --> 17:49.339
SO, I GUESS THOSE TWO MINUTES
SHE SPENT WITH YOU

17:49.339 --> 17:50.740
DIDN´T RUIN HER.

17:54.344 --> 17:57.777
WHEN ARE WE GONNA MEET HER?

17:57.777 --> 17:59.579
WE´RE NOT.

17:59.579 --> 18:02.852
SHE DOESN´T KNOW SHE´S ADOPTED,
AND I´M NOT GONNA TELL HER.

18:02.852 --> 18:04.354
GOOD.

18:04.354 --> 18:06.556
TOOK A PICTURE
OF HER, THOUGH.

18:08.218 --> 18:11.221
OH, SHE´S GOT BIG EYES.

18:11.221 --> 18:14.264
WELL, I KIND OF SURPRISED HER
WITH THE CAMERA.

18:14.264 --> 18:15.795
OH.

18:20.470 --> 18:22.132
MOM, YOU WANT TO SEE?

18:22.132 --> 18:23.873
NO.
[ TELEPHONE RINGING ]

18:23.873 --> 18:25.805
OH, I GOT IT.

18:29.379 --> 18:31.281
Angie: HELLO?

18:31.281 --> 18:32.542
HI.

18:41.251 --> 18:42.792
HMM.

18:45.755 --> 18:48.158
YOU ARE BEING SO SELFISH!

18:48.158 --> 18:50.160
HOW CAN YOU DO THIS
TO DADDY AND TO ME?!

18:50.160 --> 18:54.704
NO, I DON´T UNDERSTAND,
AND I DON´T WANT TO UNDERSTAND!

18:57.407 --> 19:00.310
SOMEONE SMELL ME.

19:06.676 --> 19:08.578
WHAT IS IT?

19:10.420 --> 19:12.652
MOM JUST CALLED.

19:12.652 --> 19:15.285
SHE´S NOT COMING.

19:16.826 --> 19:19.359
OH.

19:19.359 --> 19:20.890
DADDY.

19:23.893 --> 19:25.535
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

19:25.535 --> 19:28.268
HEY, GUYS, LOOK AT THE BLANKET
RANDY THREW OUT.

19:34.744 --> 19:36.576
HEY, HEY, HEY.
HEY, HEY.

19:36.576 --> 19:39.178
YOU ARE DOING IT ALL WRONG.

19:39.178 --> 19:41.781
LISTEN AND LEARN.

19:41.781 --> 19:45.555
DON´T PLAY IT LIKE
YOU´RE KILLING A BUG.

19:45.555 --> 19:49.219
THINK OF THE CONGAS
AS A WOMAN,

19:49.219 --> 19:54.494
AND THEN PLAY THEM LIKE
YOU´RE MAKING LOVE TO HER.

19:54.494 --> 19:56.766
[ RHYTHMIC DRUMMING ]

20:04.534 --> 20:06.606
I GOT IT.
